Patron

Which guild or planeswalker is the party's patron for this adventure?

Fronts, Rivals, Guilds

Use either the planeswalkers themselves or the guilds they represent as the main fronts, rivals or guilds in the adventure. Treat any duplicates as additional challenges or conflicts coming from that guild/faction.

Locations

The adventure should lead to these locations, good for pointcrawls. Duplicates could suggest a major change has taken place since the location was last visited.

NPCs and Creatures

Use these as NPCs or creatures

Magic Items and MacGuffins

Quest objectives, rewards, terrible threats

Enchantments

Effects currently impacting the land or major events that will happen during the adventure.

Spells

Strange effects, traps, enemy abilities, etc.
